{"tid":2292140,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「連登生存手冊」作者：衛詩","createTime":"2020-11-19T09:13:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T03:22:39.000Z","uid":272819,"like":4,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"377900c28c59944cb44d5a495d8c9106e7d65361","tid":2292140,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想係連登生存好簡單 切忌以下事情 咁就會少D負皮 <br />\n1.唔好開膠post（雖然依個post都算算地 但係都有教學性質）<br />\n<br />\n2.唔好係留言派膠，講❺毛野。（例如射精上月、石頭出糧）<br />\n<br />\n3.有圖=無圖，無圖=有圖，有大量圖=幾張圖<br />\n<br />\n4.無圖會俾連登仔放GIF（俾十秒你老母、我入到黎.gif）<br />\n<br />\n5.出左膠post會俾人狙擊（參考 棋靈王-鮑姐、爆裂鼻毛真拳3-我以後退出連登）<br />\n<br />\n6.防止標題黨，留意個標題名如果係好索好性感既名要小心（例如 衛詩既 「國色天香」可憐女子簽下賣身契）<br />\n<br />\n7.PO恐怖圖會俾連登巴絲屌爆你老母+block9你 你諗你啦（標題名有 「有圖慎入」例外）<br />\n<br />\n8.飲食台台主係衛詩（衛蘭滋潤膏無衛詩），印伯係上一代 是ex<br />\n<br />\n9.係連登講錢會變曬FG50k<br />\n<br />\n10.如果係連登打1M=1萬會俾人負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c8355d7326d98073941eb673cdab4c2604b139","tid":2292140,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:14:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"293ab357ccfb251eb7c5871b7fd833936d9469fd","tid":2292140,"uid":116917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:15:00.000Z","msg":"受教受教"},{"pid":"70d8cc995f0c22a6f99dda8a7f90f093e634122c","tid":2292140,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:15:07.000Z","msg":"記在心中了"},{"pid":"ea48cdc64903fb01e900a74f21edd70eb2559eb2","tid":2292140,"uid":281492,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:15:30.000Z","msg":"感謝大大無私